  "instructions": [
    "Wash and dry the spinach leaves; place them in a large salad bowl.",
    "In a dry skillet over medium heat, toast the almonds for 3‑4 minutes, stirring frequently, until lightly golden. Let cool.",
    "Add the diced cucumber, shredded carrots, and shredded red cabbage to the bowl.",
    "Stir in the chopped almonds.",
    "In a small bowl whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, soy sauce, honey, thyme, salt, and pepper until emulsified.",
    "Pour the dressing over the salad and toss gently to coat all ingredients.",
    "Top the salad with gherkin relish for an extra burst of tangy flavor.",
    "Serve immediately or chill in the refrigerator for up to 1 hour before serving."
